 Depth First Search

 Taking one Example

In this we will make a stack of size according to the given diagram and nodes present in it.
We can start from the starting point if provided or we can select by any point.

We will mention all the adjacent node which is related to the first point and we will put all the element in the stack in any order.
We will now pop the top most element and put in the output i.e. visited node and we will put the topmost's adjacent node in the stack and we will repeat the whole process until stack get empty and put all the value in the oout visited node.

finally we will return the answer as an output.
